result:
<!-- 编辑弹框 -->
<a-modal
  title="编辑"
  style="top: 20px;"
  :width="600"
  v-model="visible"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
  v-preventReClick
  destroyOnClose="true"
  :maskClosable="false"
>
  <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item label="地图名称" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-input
        v-decorator="[
          'mapName',
          {rules: [{ required: true, message: '请输入地图名称' }],
          initialValue: editData.mapName,}
        ]"
        placeholder="地图名称"
      />
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
